name: Genesis
description: In this piece I am seeking to express my feelings towards female sexuality and our relationship to ‘something higher’. I am often inspired by preachers on the street who state the Messiah is returning and I wonder what that would look like if he did come back. Would he emerge on the cross? Perhaps Jesus wouldn't return as a man, but a woman. The title 'Genesis' is linked to the pandemic and the coming of a new age both on a deeply personal level but also a global level. The bursting of flowers and birds in flight are there to create a sense of euphoria around the natural cycle of birth and death. Overall, life is something we should celebrate.
